<HEADLINE>
<P>
WHAT'S THE DEAL?: BODY WATCH; FOR THOSE DAYS WHEN HAIR INSISTS ON MISBEHAVING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KATHLEEN DOHENY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Bad hair days aren't funny when they hit home. The options and costs of 
cover-ups and cures: 
</P>
<P>
 * L.A. Dodgers baseball cap, $6.99. 
</P>
<P>
 * Deep conditioning treatment in untrendy salon, $10. 
</P>
<P>
 * Chin-length brown wig of human hair, $59. 
</P>
<P>
 * Chanel scarf, $250 and up. KATHLEEN DOHENY 
