<TEXT>
<P>
 A House Government Operations subcommittee announced Monday it will hold 
hearings next month on possible anti-competitive practices in the ticket 
distribution industry. 
</P>
<P>
 Subcommittee Chairman Gary A. Condit (D-Ceres) said he will invite Seattle 
