<DOCNO> LA061494-0169 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 051227 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 14, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
