</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 FTC Commissioner to Step Down: Dennis A. Yao is resigning from the Federal 
Trade Commission to return to teaching at the University of Pennsylvania. Yao 
said he will leave the commission Sept. 1, after serving three years of a 
seven-year term. The vacancy will give President Clinton his first chance to 
name a member of the commission. 
</P>
